graph TB
    subgraph WVA["Workload Variant Autoscaler"]
        direction TB
        Controller["controller-manager<br/>(Go Operator)"]
        SatEngine["Saturation Engine<br/>(30s loop)"]
        SFZEngine["Scale-from-Zero Engine<br/>(100ms poll)"]
        CMReconciler["ConfigMap Reconciler"]
        IPReconciler["InferencePool Reconciler"]
        Actuator["Actuator<br/>(Prometheus metrics emitter)"]
        DirectActuator["Direct Actuator<br/>(scale subresource patch)"]
        Collector["Collector<br/>(metrics collection)"]
        DecisionCache["Decision Cache<br/>(in-memory)"]

        SatEngine -->|collects metrics| Collector
        SatEngine -->|writes decisions| DecisionCache
        Controller -->|reads decisions| DecisionCache
        Controller -->|updates status| VACR
        SatEngine -->|emits metrics| Actuator
        SFZEngine -->|scales directly| DirectActuator
        SFZEngine -->|writes decisions| DecisionCache
        CMReconciler -->|configures| SatEngine
        CMReconciler -->|configures| SFZEngine
        IPReconciler -->|discovers EPP endpoints| SFZEngine
    end

    %% CRDs
    VACR["VariantAutoscaling CR<br/>(llmd.ai/v1alpha1)"]
    User["Platform Admin / SRE"] -->|creates| VACR
    VACR -->|watched by| Controller

    %% Metrics endpoint
    PromScrape["Prometheus Scraper"] -->|GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token| Actuator

    %% External dependencies
    Collector -->|PromQL queries<br/>9091/TCP HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token| Prometheus["Prometheus /<br/>Thanos Querier"]
    SFZEngine -->|scrape queue metrics<br/>HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token| EPP["EPP Pods<br/>(Gateway API Inference Extension)"]
    DirectActuator -->|patch scale<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API Server"]
    Controller -->|CRUD operations<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI

    %% Downstream consumers
    HPA["HPA / KEDA"] -->|reads WVA metrics<br/>via Prometheus| Prometheus
    HPA -->|scales workloads<br/>443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI

    %% Scale targets
    K8sAPI -->|scales| Deployments["Deployments /<br/>StatefulSets"]
    K8sAPI -->|scales| LWS["LeaderWorkerSets"]

    %% vLLM (indirect)
    vLLM["vLLM Inference Servers"] -->|metrics scraped by| Prometheus

    %% ConfigMaps
    ConfigMaps["ConfigMaps<br/>(saturation, scale-to-zero,<br/>queueing-model configs)"] -->|watched by| CMReconciler
    InferencePool["InferencePool CRs<br/>(v1 / v1alpha2)"] -->|watched by| IPReconciler

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SatEngine fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style SFZEngine fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style CMReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style IPReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Actuator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style DirectActuator fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Collector fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style DecisionCache fill:#6baed6,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style VACR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Prometheus fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style EPP fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style HPA fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style vLLM fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ConfigMaps fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style InferencePool fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style Deployments fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
    style LWS fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,color:#fff
